![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/96290a5e-f7f9-4e8d-a11f-7611ecd2f124/FB_IMG_1721940126889.jpg?format=original)

In a move that promises to shake up the world of superheroes, DC Comics has announced the upcoming launch of 'Justice League Unlimited', a brand-new series brought to life by the legendary writer Mark Waid and superstar artist Dan Mora.

The fresh lineup boasts an exciting mix of iconic and dynamic characters, including:

\- Superman

\- Batman

\- Flash

\- Wonder Woman

\- Captain Atom

\- Black Lightning

\- Star Sapphire

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a72e41cd-d473-4fd3-b735-37de4123c138/FB_IMG_1721940003038.jpg?format=original)

This diverse and powerful team is poised to take on the most daunting challenges in the DC Universe, and with Waid's masterful storytelling and Mora's stunning visuals, fans can expect an unforgettable adventure.

Mark Waid, known for his work on 'Kingdom Come' and 'The Flash', brings his signature blend of action, humor, and heart to the series, while Dan Mora's vibrant art style, showcased in 'Detective Comics' and 'Power Rangers', promises to bring the team to life in a way that will leave readers breathless.

'Justice League Unlimited' is set to be a game-changer for DC Comics, offering a new era of excitement and possibility for the world's greatest superheroes. Stay tuned for more updates on this highly anticipated series!